mapper.insert: INSERT INTO corona_local (createDt, deathCnt, defCnt, gubun, gubunCn, gubunEn, incDec, isolClearCnt, isolIngCnt, localOccCnt, overFlowCnt) VALUES (#{createDt}, #{deathCnt}, #{defCnt}, #{gubun}, #{gubunCn}, #{gubunEn}, #{incDec}, #{isolClearCnt}, #{isolIngCnt}, #{localOccCnt}, #{overFlowCnt});
